</span></span></span><![endif]><b style=3D'mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'>Car=
go</b>:
all resources and components stored at this colony, including which empire =
owns
the cargo</p>

<p class=3DMsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle style=3D'text-indent:-.25in;mso-list:=
l0 level1 lfo2'><![if !supportLists]><span
