ies
under construction</p>

<p class=3DMsoNormal>The name of the colony is displayed at the middle-righ=
t of
the screen. The name can be changed by typing a new one.</p>

<p class=3DMsoNormal>The tax rate for the colony is shown underneath the na=
me.
Type a new value here to change the tax rate. Note that if you have automat=
ed
the control of colony tax rates <span class=3DSpellE>then</span> any change=
s that
you make here could be overridden later.</p>

